## ‚öôÔ∏è Configuration

You can easily adjust the bot's behavior by modifying the constants at the top of `cookie_bot.py`:

```python
# ============================================================
# CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================

CLICK_INTERVAL = 0.0001      # How fast the cookie is clicked (affects lag!)
UPGRADE_INTERVAL = 0.5       # How often to check/buy upgrades
BUILD_INTERVAL = 1.5         # How often to check/buy the best building
RUN_MINUTES = 5              # Total run time
# ... and so on
